sketch.compiler.ast.core.typs

Class TypeArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.typs.Type
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.typs.TypeArray

  • public class TypeArray
extends Type
    A homogenous array type with a length. This type has a base type and an expression for the length. The expression must be of integer type, but may contain variables.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    David Maze <dmaze@cag.lcs.mit.edu> modified by Armando Solar-Lezama

        public TypeArray(Type base,
                 Expression length,
                 java.util.Collection<Expression> dims)
        Create an array with the given base type, length, and dimensions. It is assumed, but not checked, that \product{dims} = length.
        Parameters:
        base - base type of the array
        length - number of elements of the base type
        dims - the "virtual dimensions" of the array
